v8.0 - Added flag to automatically open a midi port to Hydrogen if it's
running

v7.0 - Fixed bug when multiple pads are held down simultaneously.

v6.0 - Conditional compilation so it will build without ALSA, Jack or SDL
installed. Signal handling for orderly shutdown of ALSA and SDL_Mixer

v5.0 - Jack Support, Samples path uses ${prefix} now

v4.0 - Autoconf/Automake

v3.0 - ALSA MIDI support. Can now connect to Hydrogen and play first six drum
sounds

v2.0 - Put samples in /usrshare/drumroll

v1.0 - Initial Release
